(add-tip "The more workers you have collecting resources, the faster your economy will grow.")
(add-tip "Building more than one barracks will let you train more units faster.")
(add-tip "Use your workers to repair damaged buildings.")
(add-tip "Explore your surroundings early in the game.")

(add-tip "You can demolish trees and rocks.")
(add-tip "Keep all workers working. Use ALT-I to find idle workers.")
(add-tip "You can make units automatically cast spells by selecting a unit, holding down CTRL and clicking on the spell icon.  CTRL click again to turn off.")

;; Shift tips
(add-tip "You can give an unit an order which is executed after it finishes the current work, if you hold the SHIFT key.")
(add-tip "You can give way points, if you press the SHIFT key, while you click right for the move command.")
(add-tip "You can order a worker to build one building after the other, if you hold the SHIFT key, while you place the building.");
(add-tip "You can build many of the same building, if you hold the ALT and SHIFT keys while you place the buildings.")

(add-tip "Use CTRL-V or ALT-V to cycle through the viewport configuration, you can than monitor your base and lead an attack.")

